job.title: NTPC  Engineering Executive  Recruitment  2021 – Apply Online for 280 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:280

Name of the Posts:

  • Graduate Engineers
  • Engineering Executive Trainee (EET)

Description

New Central Government Jobs for Engineers has been published by National Thermal Power Corporation Limited for the vacancies of Engineering Executive. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the post of Engineering Executive, from 18.05.2021, and till 10.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for an Engineering Executive vacancies in India, your Engineering must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these vacancies is 18.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these vacancies is 10.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 37  years old. 

NTPC Engineering Executive Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Indian Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 40,000 – 1, 40,000/-.

How to apply for NTPC Engineering Executive Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Engineering Executive. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of NTPC  and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by NTPC.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
